# Project memory

## Architecture

- API v2 is canonical; v1 endpoints are deprecated
- Runnable services live under components/<name>/

## Procedures

- Run component validation with tests/run_validation.py
- Root integration uses deploy/local/launch-gem.ps1 with GEM_SYSTEM_DATA_DIR set

## Constraints

- Do not use EnsureCreated() for database upgrades; use EF Core migrations at the app layer when applicable
